 <div class="post-1949 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-uncategorized" id="post-1949">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on June 18, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1949">Winnerrrsss [UPDATED]</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" title="contests1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" alt="" width="312" height="50" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/ekolokoMoon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1825" title="ekolokoMoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/ekolokoMoon.jpg" alt="" width="532" height="43" /></a></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">[UPDATE]</span></strong> Attention all those who participated in the contest but <span style="color: #008000;"><em>did not</em></span> win. Please see your inventory to find a special gift from me. ~<span style="color: #800080;"><strong>IzzyRo</strong></span></p>
<p>This was a <span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>~HOT<strong>~</strong></strong></span> competition! Thank you to all the ekos who participated.</p>
<p>Here are our <strong><span style="color: #800080;">Lucky 11 winners</span></strong>. Our winners did something different varying in creativity, simplicity, organization, technique, etc. Here they are:</p>
<div id="attachment_1951" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 594px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/amiyoy7Summer.jpg" ><img class="size-large wp-image-1951" title="amiyoy7Summer" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/amiyoy7Summer-1024x642.jpg" alt="" width="584" height="366" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">amiyoy7 - Summer Vacation</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1952" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 594px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/avrila-Ice-cream-Summer.jpg" ><img class="size-large wp-image-1952" title="avrila Ice cream Summer" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/avrila-Ice-cream-Summer-1024x516.jpg" alt="" width="584" height="294" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">avrila - Summer with Ice Cream</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1953" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 594px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Butterfly-Shiny-Sun.png" ><img class="size-large wp-image-1953" title="Butterfly Shiny Sun" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Butterfly-Shiny-Sun-1024x641.png" alt="" width="584" height="365" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Butterfly - Shiny Sun</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1954" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 878px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Facehole-Sunny-Summer-Fun.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1954" title="Facehole Sunny Summer Fun" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Facehole-Sunny-Summer-Fun.png" alt="" width="868" height="521" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Facehole - Sunny Summer Fun</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1955" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 594px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Goldstar-Summer-Beach-Bar.png" ><img class="size-large wp-image-1955" title="Goldstar Summer Beach Bar" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Goldstar-Summer-Beach-Bar-1024x582.png" alt="" width="584" height="331" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Goldstar - Summer Beach Bar</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1956" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 705px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/maayan34-Beach-Towels.jpg" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1956" title="maayan34 Beach Towels" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/maayan34-Beach-Towels.jpg" alt="" width="695" height="479" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">maayan34 - Beach Fun</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1961" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 1010px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/matan078-Summer-Fun-House.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1961" title="matan078 Summer Fun House" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/matan078-Summer-Fun-House.png" alt="" width="1000" height="588" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">matan078 - Summer Fun House</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1957" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 909px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Maximum-Tulip.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1957" title="Maximum Tulip" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Maximum-Tulip.png" alt="" width="899" height="603" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Maximum - Pool Party</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1958" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 594px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Mazaii-Cooling-Off-with-Music.png" ><img class="size-large wp-image-1958 " title="Mazaii Cooling Off with Music" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Mazaii-Cooling-Off-with-Music-1024x456.png" alt="" width="584" height="260" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">mazaii - Summer Breeze</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1959" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 793px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/omriliz-On-the-Beach-with-Music.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1959" title="omriliz On the Beach with Music" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/omriliz-On-the-Beach-with-Music.png" alt="" width="783" height="409" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">omriliz - Music on the Beach</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1960" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 875px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/sagi9949-Friends-in-Summer.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1960" title="sagi9949 Friends in Summer" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/sagi9949-Friends-in-Summer.png" alt="" width="865" height="542" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">sagi9949 - Summer With Friends</p></div>
<p><strong><span style="color: #99cc00;">C<span style="color: #0000ff;">o</span><span style="color: #ff00ff;">n</span><span style="color: #800080;">g</span>r<span style="color: #00ccff;">a</span><span style="color: #ff0000;">t</span><span style="color: #666699;">u</span><span style="color: #ff9900;">l</span><span style="color: #800000;">a</span><span style="color: #cc99ff;">t</span>i<span style="color: #008000;">o</span><span style="color: #008080;">n</span><span style="color: #ff00ff;">s</span><span style="color: #ff0000;">!!!</span></span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #ff00ff;">Winners:</span></strong> Please email <strong><span style="color: #0000ff;">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</span></strong> to claim your prize!</p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
