 <div class="post-1935 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-uncategorized" id="post-1935">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on June 11, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1935">Summer Nights</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" title="contests1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" alt="" width="312" height="50" /></a></p>
<p>It’s almost Summer time and to celebrate…we are having a new <span style="color: #666699;"><strong>MOON HOUSE COMPETITION!</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;"><strong>Here is what you need to know:</strong></span></p>
<p>1. You must decorate your moon with a <span style="color: #33cccc;">SUMMER</span> theme in YOUR style.</p>
<p>2. You can start decorating your moon NOW!</p>
<p>3. When your moon is finished you must take a picture of your moon <span style="color: #ff00ff;"><strong>with your eko standing inside</strong></span> so that I know it is your house.</p>
<p>4. You ARE allowed to use any photo editing software…but ONLY a little! Using a LOT of special graphics will NOT help you win. Not everyone knows how to use that software.</p>
<p>5. You must send your picture to <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>usa_blog@ekoloko.com</strong></span> by the end of <strong><span style="color: #008000;">Sunday, June 16th.</span></strong></p>
<p>I will announce the winners by the end of <strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">Monday, June 17th</span></strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">.</span></p>
<p>There will be prizes for both pioneers and non-pioneers so everyone will have a fair chance to win.</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">ALSO &#8212; Please remember to SAVE your arrangements many times! If you spend too much time arranging without saving, it might not save and you will have to design your house all over again. So remember&#8230;SAVE SAVE and SAVE again! </span></strong></p>
<p>Good luck!!! I am so excited to see your moons! Please remember to send your picture of your completed moon to <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>usa_blog@ekoloko.com</strong></span>.</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/ekoParty.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1914" title="ekoParty" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/ekoParty.png" alt="" width="95" height="102" /></a></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=8" title="View all posts in Contests" rel="category">Contests</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category">Uncategorized</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1935#comments" title="Comment on Summer Nights">10 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1928 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekoart" id="post-1928">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on June 6, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1928">More art for you!</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<div id="attachment_1929" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 316px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MrsYuvalPic.jpg" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1929" title="MrsYuvalPic" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MrsYuvalPic.jpg" alt="" width="306" height="306" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">MrsYuval</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1930" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 1034px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/amiyoy7Pic.jpg" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1930" title="amiyoy7Pic" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/amiyoy7Pic.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">amiyoy7</p></div>
<p>Thank you for sending me your art. I&#8217;m always so impressed!</p>
<p>Remember, everything is art! You can even send me some nice screen shots of you and your friends playing in ekoloko. I love to see you having fun.</p>
<p>Send your art to <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>usa_blog@ekoloko.com</strong></span></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1928#comments" title="Comment on More art for you!">5 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1911 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-rangers" id="post-1911">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on June 2, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1911">Congratulations New Rangerssssss</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>We just finished our <span style="color: #339966;"><strong>Ranger Ceremony</strong></span> and it was great!</p>
<p><span style="color: #ff0000;">EVERY NEW RANGER ATTENDED!!!!</span></p>
<p><a style="font-size: 13px;" href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/ekoCrazy.png" ><img class="wp-image-1912 alignnone" title="ekoCrazy" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/ekoCrazy.png" alt="" width="78" height="98" /></a><a style="font-size: 13px;" href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/ekoThumbsup.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1913 alignnone" title="ekoThumbsup" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/ekoThumbsup.png" alt="" width="73" height="81" /></a><img class="wp-image-1914 alignnone" style="font-size: 13px;" title="ekoParty" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/ekoParty.png" alt="" width="95" height="102" /></p>
<p>Congratulations to: <strong><span style="color: #800080;">ChaoticMonki, georgia9391, guy2guy2, ido2409, MrsYuval, shovalmotek, and webgoldi2!!!</span></strong></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/RangerCeremony6-2-13.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1915" title="RangerCeremony6-2-13" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/RangerCeremony6-2-13.jpg" alt="" width="999" height="454" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1911#comments" title="Comment on Congratulations New Rangerssssss">16 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1898 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized" id="post-1898">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on May 27, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1898">Rangerrrrrsss&#8230;</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>I am happy to announce our newest group of Advanced Rangers: <span style="color: #800080;"><strong>ChaoticMonki, georgia9391, guy2guy2, ido2409, MrsYuval, and shovalmotek!!!</strong></span></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/RangersJune2_2013.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1899" title="RangersJune2_2013" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/RangersJune2_2013.png" alt="" width="989" height="329" /></a></p>
<p>Invited from last week: <span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>webgoldi2</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #339966;">All Advanced Rangers are invited to the ceremony!</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>WHEN</strong>:</span> Sunday, June 2 at 2pm EDT, 21:00 Israel, 20:00 France</p>
<p><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>WHERE</strong>:</span> The best world EVER: ekoloko&#8230;any room&#8230;you&#8217;ll see a message <img src='http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_razz.gif' alt=':-P' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
<p>If you can&#8217;t come to your ceremony please email <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>support_us@ekoloko.com</strong></span><strong> </strong></p>
<p><span style="color: #993366;"><strong>Congrats new Rangers!!!</strong></span></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category">Uncategorized</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1898#comments" title="Comment on Rangerrrrrsss&#8230;">15 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1883 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-ekoart category-ekonews category-events category-uncategorized" id="post-1883">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on May 24, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1883">The Party Isn&#8217;t Over</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-120" title="news title1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/news-title11.png" alt="" width="339" height="63" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/HappyBirthdayekoloko.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1884" title="HappyBirthdayekoloko" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/HappyBirthdayekoloko.png" alt="" width="685" height="274" /></a></p>
<p>So&#8230;you think the <span style="color: #333399;">moon contest</span> was fun? Well, we have a very special <span style="color: #ff00ff;">ekoloko Birthday Festival</span> coming up&#8230; So keep checking the blog for updates.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-419" title="EkoArt title" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/EkoArt-title.png" alt="" width="250" height="90" /></a></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">I have been getting a lot of different styles of art for the blog!  Take a look:</span></p>
<div id="attachment_1885" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 822px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/selenatorArt.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1885" title="selenatorArt" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/selenatorArt.png" alt="" width="812" height="600" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">selenator</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1886" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 650px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Koksiboy-happybirthday-graffiti-jpg.jpg" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1886" title="Koksiboy happybirthday-graffiti-jpg" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Koksiboy-happybirthday-graffiti-jpg.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="304" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">koksiboy</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1887" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 1034px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/PonPon447-logo_2.jpg" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1887" title="PonPon447 logo_2" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/PonPon447-logo_2.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="768" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">PonPon447</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1888" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 610px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Jessica631Pic.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1888" title="Jessica631Pic" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Jessica631Pic.png" alt="" width="600" height="700" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Jessica631</p></div>
<p>Thanks everyone for sending in your beautiful art. If you want to share your art on the blog please send your files to <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>usa_blog@ekoloko.com!</strong></span></p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=11" title="View all posts in EkoArt" rel="category">EkoArt</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=3" title="View all posts in EkoNews" rel="category">EkoNews</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=6" title="View all posts in Events" rel="category">Events</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category">Uncategorized</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1883#comments" title="Comment on The Party Isn&#8217;t Over">3 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1847 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-uncategorized" id="post-1847">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on May 20, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1847">Contest Winnerssssss</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-122" title="contests1" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/contests1.png" alt="" width="312" height="50" /></a></p>
<p>I want to thank everyone who entered the <strong><span style="color: #008000;">ekoloko</span> <span style="color: #ff0000;">One</span>-<span style="color: #000080;">Year</span> <span style="color: #ff00ff;">Birthday</span> <span style="color: #ff6600;">Moon</span> <span style="color: #3366ff;">House</span></strong> Contest.</p>
<p>I received almost <span style="color: #800080;"><strong>60</strong></span> pictures and I loved ALL of them&#8230;but alas&#8230;there can only be a handful of winners&#8230; So here they are!</p>
<div id="attachment_1857" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 594px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/avrila-moon.jpg" ><img class="size-large wp-image-1857" title="avrila moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/avrila-moon-1024x480.jpg" alt="" width="584" height="273" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">avrila</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1858" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 911px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Chiwawa-moon.png" ><img class="size-full wp-image-1858" title="Chiwawa moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Chiwawa-moon.png" alt="" width="901" height="540" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Chiwawa</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1859" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 594px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Cinnamon-moon.jpg" ><img class=" wp-image-1859" title="Cinnamon moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Cinnamon-moon-1024x600.jpg" alt="" width="584" height="342" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Cinnamon</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1860" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 594px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Dancing4lyfe-moon.png" ><img class=" wp-image-1860" title="Dancing4lyfe moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Dancing4lyfe-moon-1024x532.png" alt="" width="584" height="303" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Dancing4lyfe</p></div>
<div class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 728px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Dracula-moon.png" ><img title="Dracula moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Dracula-moon.png" alt="" width="718" height="442" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Dracula</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1861" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 963px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/guy2guy2-moon.gif" ><img class=" wp-image-1861" title="guy2guy2 moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/guy2guy2-moon.gif" alt="" width="953" height="594" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">guy2guy2</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1862" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 594px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Jessica631-moon.png" ><img class="size-large wp-image-1862" title="Jessica631 moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Jessica631-moon-1024x767.png" alt="" width="584" height="437" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Jessica631</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1863" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 981px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/LeBron-moon.bmp" ><img class=" wp-image-1863" title="LeBron moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/LeBron-moon.bmp" alt="" width="971" height="600" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">LeBron</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1864" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 594px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/MasterShef1-moon.png" ><img class=" wp-image-1864" title="MasterShef1 moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/MasterShef1-moon-1024x559.png" alt="" width="584" height="318" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">MasterShef1</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1865" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 972px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Maximum-moon.png" ><img class=" wp-image-1865" title="Maximum moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Maximum-moon.png" alt="" width="962" height="600" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Maximum</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1866" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 968px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/missions-moon.png" ><img class=" wp-image-1866" title="missions moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/missions-moon.png" alt="" width="958" height="599" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">missions</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1867" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 971px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Rajveer-moon.png" ><img class=" wp-image-1867" title="Rajveer moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Rajveer-moon.png" alt="" width="961" height="602" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Rajveer</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1868" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 871px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Random132-moon.png" ><img class=" wp-image-1868" title="Random132 moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Random132-moon.png" alt="" width="861" height="522" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Random132</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1869" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 970px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/taleko-moon.jpg" ><img class=" wp-image-1869" title="taleko moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/taleko-moon.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="542" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">taleko</p></div>
<div id="attachment_1870" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="width: 969px"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/YuvalXD-moon.png" ><img class=" wp-image-1870" title="YuvalXD  moon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/YuvalXD-moon.png" alt="" width="959" height="527" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">YuvalXD</p></div>
<div class="mceTemp"><span style="color: #00ccff;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong style="color: #ff6600; font-size: 13px; text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #ff00ff; text-decoration: underline;">Congratulations</span><span style="color: #3366ff; text-decoration: underline;"> to the</span> <span style="color: #ff00ff; text-decoration: underline;">winners</span>! </strong></span></em></span></div>
<p><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Attention winners:</strong></span> Please email <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>usa_blog@ekoloko.com</strong> <span style="color: #000000;">to claim your prize. I will give you two options for a prize.</span></span></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">Attention to all who entered but did not win:</span></strong> Everyone designed such awesome moons that I decided I wanted to give everyone something special <strong><span style="color: #008000;">just for trying</span></strong>. So please look in your inventories to find your gift!</p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
