 <div class="post-1843 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized" id="post-1843">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on May 20, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1843">Ranger Ceremony</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p>Congratulations to our new <strong><span style="color: #008000;">Rangers</span></strong> who were promoted yesterday. In case you weren&#8217;t at the ceremony&#8230;have a look!</p>
<p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Ranger-Power-5-19-13.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1844" title="Ranger Power 5-19-13" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/Ranger-Power-5-19-13.png" alt="" width="1115" height="457" /></a></p>
<p>Congratulations to <span style="color: #800080;"><strong>ariel1808, JinJer, loIipop, PoniStyle, selenator, and zogov123!!!</strong></span></p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Absent:</span></strong> <span style="color: #ff6600;"><strong>webgoldi2</strong></span> &#8212; I&#8217;m sorry you couldn&#8217;t make it. You are welcome to join the ceremony in 2 weeks. <img src='http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category">Uncategorized</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1843#comments" title="Comment on Ranger Ceremony">17 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1837 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-rangers" id="post-1837">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on May 17, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1837">Ranger Ceremony Update!</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-14" title="rangers of the week header" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/rangers-of-the-week-header.png" alt="" width="625" height="62" /></a></p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;">Helloooo, Rangerrrrrss! As I said before, the time of your ceremony might be changed&#8230;and it has:</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;">Your ceremony will now be at this time: </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ff0000; font-size: 13px;">Sunday, May 19th at </span><strong style="color: #ff0000; font-size: 13px;">11am EDT, 6pm Israel, 5pm France.</strong></p>
<p><span style="color: #800080;">Please email</span> <strong><span style="color: #0000ff;">usa_blog@ekoloko.com</span></strong> <span style="color: #800080;">if you have any questions.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=7" title="View all posts in Rangers" rel="category">Rangers</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1837#comments" title="Comment on Ranger Ceremony Update!">5 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 <div class="post-1823 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-contests category-uncategorized" id="post-1823">
 <p class="postmetadataw">Posted by: <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?author=1" title="Posts by admin" rel="author">admin</a> | on May 16, 2013</p>		
 <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1823">**Update** Birthday Moon House Contest!!!</a></h2>
 <div class="content-ver-sep"> </div>
 <div class="entrytext">
  <p><a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/ekolokoMoon.jpg" ><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1825" title="ekolokoMoon" src="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/ekolokoMoon.jpg" alt="" width="532" height="43" /></a></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13px;">We are celebrating </span><span style="font-size: 13px; color: #339966;"><strong>ekoloko USA&#8217;s</strong></span><span style="font-size: 13px;"> 1-year birthday!!! What does that mean? </span><span style="font-size: 13px; color: #800080;"><strong>MOON HOUSE CONTEST TIME!</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #993300;"><strong>Here is what you need to know:</strong></span></p>
<p>1. You must decorate your moon with an ekoloko birthday theme in YOUR style.</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">2. Ekos have been asking me about Photoshop: </span></strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">You ARE allowed to use any photo editing software&#8230;but ONLY a little! Using a LOT of special graphics will NOT help you win. Not everyone knows how to use that software.</span></p>
<p>3. You can start decorating your moon <strong><span style="color: #003300;">NOW</span></strong>!</p>
<p>4. When your moon is finished you must take a picture of your moon <span style="color: #ff00ff;"><strong>with your eko standing inside</strong></span> so that I know it is your house.</p>
<p>5. Send your picture to <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>usa_blog@ekoloko.com</strong></span> by the end of <strong><span style="color: #ff6600;">Sunday, May 19th</span></strong>.</p>
<p>I will announce the winners by the end of <strong><span style="color: #993300;">Monday, May 20th</span></strong>.</p>
<p>There will be prizes for both pioneers and non-pioneers so everyone will have a fair chance to win.</p>
<p>Good luck!!! I am so excited to see your moons! Please remember to send your picture of your completed moon to <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>usa_blog@ekoloko.com</strong></span>.</p>
 <div class="clear"> </div>
 <div class="up-bottom-border">
 <p class="postmetadata">Posted in <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=8" title="View all posts in Contests" rel="category">Contests</a>, <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?cat=1" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category">Uncategorized</a> |   <a href="http://blog.us.ekoloko.com/?p=1823#comments" title="Comment on **Update** Birthday Moon House Contest!!!">14 Comments &#187;</a> </p>
 </div>
 </div></div>
 
 
